# BlockID.au — Production Cron Schedule (Single Source of Truth)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# All times in UTC. Server in UTC, users in AEST (UTC+10).
#
# IMPORTANT: Edit THIS file, then apply with:
#   crontab /home/dovanlong/blockid.au/web/scripts/crontab.production
#
# All API endpoints use cron-runner.sh for:
#   ✅ Logging every run to /tmp/blockid-cron.log
#   ✅ Structured health log → content/reports/cron-health.jsonl
#   ✅ Telegram alert on failure
#   ✅ Auto log rotation (200KB cap)

# CRON_SECRET is no longer set here — cron-runner.sh reads it from the gitignored
# web/.env at runtime (keeps the secret out of version control). Set it in .env.
RUN=/home/dovanlong/blockid.au/web/scripts/cron-runner.sh

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SYSTEM — Infrastructure (no AI)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Watchdog — auto-restart if production is dead
*/2 * * * * /home/dovanlong/blockid.au/web/scripts/watchdog.sh

# Cloudflare DDNS — keep DNS pointing to this server
*/5 * * * * /usr/local/bin/cloudflare-ddns-update.sh >> /var/log/cloudflare-ddns.log 2>&1

# AI token guardian — refresh Claude OAuth + provider keys
*/30 * * * * /home/dovanlong/blockid.au/web/scripts/ai-token-guardian.sh >> /tmp/ai-guardian.log 2>&1

# Token refresh — OAuth tokens (Google, GitHub, etc.)
0 */4 * * * /home/dovanlong/blockid.au/scripts/refresh-tokens.sh >> /tmp/blockid-token-refresh.log 2>&1

# Blockchain sync — process DB queue (no AI)
*/15 * * * * bash $RUN blockchain-sync

# AI health check — test provider availability (no AI calls)
0 */3 * * * bash $RUN ai-health

# Auto-Guardian — monitor thresholds, auto-fix at 80%, alert on critical
*/10 * * * * bash $RUN agent-guardian --timeout 90

# Auto-deploy — ONLY at off-peak AEST so users aren't impacted (was every 30m).
# Push local commits + pull GitHub + deploy new commits.
0 18 * * * /home/dovanlong/blockid.au/web/scripts/git-sync-deploy.sh

# Autonomous self-upgrade — Claude Code SUBSCRIPTION (not API). Implements one
# low-risk improvement, gated deploy + revert-on-failure. 04:30 AEST (off-peak).
30 18 * * * bash /home/dovanlong/blockid.au/web/scripts/self-upgrade-agent.sh >> /tmp/blockid-self-upgrade.log 2>&1

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DAILY PIPELINE — 2am-10:30am AEST (4pm-12:30am+1 UTC)
#
# Goal: Auto-upgrade → check → fix → deploy → verify → report
# Optimized for continuous improvement throughout the day
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Phase 1: Data Collection (2:00-2:30am AEST / 16:xx UTC) ──
0 16 * * * bash $RUN svi-snapshot
5 16 * * * bash $RUN svi-notify
10 16 * * * bash $RUN nurture
15 16 * * * bash $RUN vesting

# ── Phase 2: Health & Metrics (3:00am AEST / 17:00 UTC) ──────
0 17 * * * bash $RUN agent-upgrade --timeout 120

# ── Phase 3: Intelligence (4:00-6:00am AEST / 18-20 UTC) ─────
0 18 * * * bash $RUN growth-insights --timeout 120
0 19 * * * bash $RUN svi-review
0 20 * * * bash $RUN agent-research --timeout 300

# ── Phase 4: Auto-Improve + CI/CD (7:00am AEST / 21:00 UTC) ──
0 21 * * * bash $RUN agent-auto-improve --timeout 300
5 21 * * * bash $RUN refresh-models
30 21 * * * bash $RUN publish-insight --timeout 120

# ── Phase 5: QA + Security + Performance (8:00am AEST) ────────
0 22 * * * bash $RUN agent-healthcheck --timeout 180

# ── Phase 6: Reporting (8:30-10:00am AEST) ────────────────────
# Daily admin report — platform KPIs + email
30 22 * * * bash $RUN daily-admin-report

# Daily traffic + funnel report (GA4 traffic + internal funnel) → email + Telegram
30 22 * * * bash $RUN traffic-report --timeout 120

# Telegram daily report — C-Level agent status
30 23 * * * bash $RUN telegram-report

# CEO Daily Summary — aggregates ALL agent reports + AI recommendations
# Runs LAST at 10:00am AEST, after all agents have reported
0 0 * * * bash $RUN ceo-daily-summary --timeout 120

# ── Phase 7: Self-Healing (10:30am AEST) ──────────────────────
30 0 * * * bash $RUN cron-health

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ORCHESTRATOR — Leader Agent (CEO implementing-plan loop)
# Pipeline: research → plan(CEO) → code → deploy → update_artifacts → qa → report
# 24/7 SAFETY: the orchestrator gates deploy-causing stages (code, deploy) to
# off-peak via isOffPeakHours() (AEST 22:00–06:00 = UTC 12:00–20:00). All runs
# below are scheduled inside that window so shipping never hits peak traffic.
# Research / CEO planning / artifact recording / reporting are content-only.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Off-peak only: 10pm, 12am, 2am, 4am AEST (12,14,16,18 UTC) — full daily pipeline
0 12 * * * bash $RUN agent-orchestrator --timeout 300
0 14 * * * bash $RUN agent-orchestrator --timeout 300
0 16 * * * bash $RUN agent-orchestrator --timeout 300
0 18 * * * bash $RUN agent-orchestrator --timeout 300

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AFTERNOON: Second Pass (2:00-4:00pm AEST / 4-6am UTC)
# Use remaining Claude Code limits for continuous improvement
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Second agent-healthcheck — catch issues from morning deploys
0 8 * * * bash $RUN agent-healthcheck --timeout 180

# Second auto-improve pass — apply any remaining research
30 8 * * * bash $RUN agent-auto-improve --timeout 300

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# WEEKLY — Sunday only
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# 6:30am AEST Sunday — Lifecycle follow-up emails
30 20 * * 0 bash $RUN weekly-insights --timeout 120

# 3:00am AEST Sunday (17:00 UTC Sat) — Disk cleanup (nested releases, npm cache, /tmp, Docker)
0 17 * * 0 bash /home/dovanlong/blockid.au/web/scripts/clean-disk.sh --apply >> /tmp/blockid-clean-disk.log 2>&1

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PIPELINE FLOW DIAGRAM
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# MORNING CYCLE (2am-10:30am AEST):
#   ┌─ Phase 1: Data ──────────────┐
#   │ svi-snapshot, svi-notify     │
#   │ nurture, vesting             │
#   └──────────┬───────────────────┘
#              ▼
#   ┌─ Phase 2: Health ────────────┐
#   │ agent-upgrade (metrics+reports│
#   └──────────┬───────────────────┘
#              ▼
#   ┌─ Phase 3: Intelligence ──────┐
#   │ growth-insights              │
#   │ svi-review                   │
#   │ agent-research (AI)          │
#   └──────────┬───────────────────┘
#              ▼
#   ┌─ Phase 4: Auto-Improve ─────┐
#   │ agent-auto-improve (AI)      │
#   │ → read research              │
#   │ → generate code              │
#   │ → CI gates (tsc/lint)        │
#   │ → autofix if fail            │
#   │ → deploy-live.sh             │
#   │ → push to GitHub             │
#   │ refresh-models               │
#   │ publish-insight              │
#   └──────────┬───────────────────┘
#              ▼
#   ┌─ Phase 5: QA Verify ────────┐
#   │ agent-healthcheck            │
#   │ → TypeScript + ESLint        │
#   │ → Security (SSL, headers)    │
#   │ → Performance (mem, CPU)     │
#   │ → Infrastructure (DB, Redis) │
#   │ → Maintenance (clean logs)   │
#   │ → Email + Telegram report    │
#   └──────────┬───────────────────┘
#              ▼
#   ┌─ Phase 6: Reporting ────────┐
#   │ daily-admin-report (email)   │
#   │ telegram-report              │
#   │ ceo-daily-summary            │ ◄── NEW: CEO aggregates ALL
#   │ → reads all agent reports    │
#   │ → AI analysis + recs         │
#   │ → email + Telegram           │
#   └──────────┬───────────────────┘
#              ▼
#   ┌─ Phase 7: Self-Healing ─────┐
#   │ cron-health                  │
#   └──────────────────────────────┘
#
# ORCHESTRATOR CYCLE (8x daily, every 2h spread):
#   ┌─ Agent Orchestrator ─────────┐
#   │ Leader/Manager pattern:      │
#   │ 1. research (knowledge)      │
#   │ 2. plan (AI priorities)      │
#   │ 3. phase_upgrade (progress)  │
#   │ 4. code (auto-improve)       │
#   │ 5. build_test (verify)       │
#   │ 6. qa (healthcheck)          │
#   │ 7. fix (auto-remediate)      │
#   │ 8. report (Telegram)         │
#   │ Budget-aware: spreads calls  │
#   │ evenly across subscription   │
#   └──────────────────────────────┘
#
# AFTERNOON CYCLE (6pm AEST):
#   ┌─ Second Pass ────────────────┐
#   │ agent-healthcheck (6pm)      │
#   │ agent-auto-improve (6:30pm)  │
#   │ → use remaining AI budget    │
#   └──────────────────────────────┘
#
# CONTINUOUS:
#   ┌─ Auto-Guardian (every 10m) ──┐
#   │ 9 metrics: disk, mem, CPU,   │
#   │ inodes, swap, node RSS,      │
#   │ open FDs, zombies, /tmp      │
#   │ ≥80% → auto-fix + re-check  │
#   │ ≥95% → aggressive cleanup   │
#   │ → Telegram + Email alert     │
#   └──────────────────────────────┘
#   git-sync-deploy (every 30m) — GitHub ↔ server sync
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SCHEDULE SUMMARY (34+ routines)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Time (AEST)     | Job                | AI  | Phase        | Monitored
# ────────────────┼────────────────────┼─────┼──────────────┼──────────
# Every 2m        | watchdog           | 0   | system       | PID+HTTP
# Every 5m        | cloudflare-ddns    | 0   | system       | logfile
# Every 10m       | agent-guardian     | 0   | auto-heal    | ✅ runner
# Every 15m       | blockchain-sync    | 0   | system       | ✅ runner
# Every 30m       | ai-token-guardian  | 0   | system       | logfile
# Every 30m       | git-sync-deploy    | 0   | CI/CD        | logfile
# Every 3h        | ai-health          | 0   | system       | ✅ runner
# Every 4h        | token-refresh      | 0   | system       | logfile
# 12am,2am,4am    | orchestrator (AM)  | 1-3 | orchestrate  | ✅ runner
# 12pm,2pm,4pm    | orchestrator (PM)  | 1-3 | orchestrate  | ✅ runner
# 8pm,10pm        | orchestrator (EVE) | 1-3 | orchestrate  | ✅ runner
# 2:00am          | svi-snapshot       | 0   | data         | ✅ runner
# 2:05am          | svi-notify         | 0   | data         | ✅ runner
# 2:10am          | nurture            | 0   | data         | ✅ runner
# 2:15am          | vesting            | 0   | data         | ✅ runner
# 3:00am          | agent-upgrade      | 0-3 | health       | ✅ runner
# 4:00am          | growth-insights    | 0-1 | intelligence | ✅ runner
# 5:00am          | svi-review         | 0   | intelligence | ✅ runner
# 6:00am          | agent-research     | 1-3 | intelligence | ✅ runner
# 7:00am          | agent-auto-improve | 1-3 | auto-deploy  | ✅ runner
# 7:05am          | refresh-models     | 0   | auto-deploy  | ✅ runner
# 7:30am          | publish-insight    | 0-1 | auto-deploy  | ✅ runner
# 8:00am          | agent-healthcheck  | 0   | QA/security  | ✅ runner
# 8:30am          | daily-admin-report | 0-1 | reporting    | ✅ runner
# 9:30am          | telegram-report    | 0   | reporting    | ✅ runner
# 10:00am         | ceo-daily-summary  | 0-1 | CEO report   | ✅ runner
# 10:30am         | cron-health        | 0   | self-heal    | ✅ runner
# 6:00pm          | agent-healthcheck  | 0   | QA (2nd)     | ✅ runner
# 6:30pm          | agent-auto-improve | 1-3 | auto (2nd)   | ✅ runner
# 6:30am (Sun)    | weekly-insights    | 0-1 | weekly       | ✅ runner
# ────────────────┼────────────────────┼─────┼──────────────┼──────────
# Total AI/day: 12-30 calls | Budget-aware: auto-throttles
# Orchestrator: research→plan→upgrade→code→test→deploy→QA→fix→report
# CI/CD: auto-improve → tsc → lint → autofix → deploy-live → GitHub
# Reports: Telegram (real-time) + Email (daily) + CEO summary
